Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.14,Date,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zenkai Girl" Episode 11 - Final - (19 Sept 2011)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this. It's a pill bug good-luck bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pill bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always carry it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you text messages and look at the night's first sky every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm... see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, why are you crying? I'm not going to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So dad, never cry again. If you do cry, then cry when you are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when I'm happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah! I forgot something!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right, shall we go?\N- Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gift he left behind must be his smiles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pitaro! See you again!\N- Dad! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zenkai Girl" [Full-throttle Girl]{\b1} Final{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.77,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuba's Mori Preschool
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning.\N- Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh! What a pretty smile.\N- Hi, Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitaro's dad won't come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow it feels rather lonely. Right, Ayukawa?\N- No, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one less child to on the after-school care rotation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! I found a pill bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A pill bug?\N- They're kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now there is only one thing that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to you. It's about Ms. Sakurakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain to you that this industry doesn't need warm sentiments. Ms. Sakurakawa is aware of that herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But I'm sure that the hand that will reach out to you is...\N- It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the continuation of the contract with our firm's main client, Brighton Holdings, as you're aware, we have received a proposal to place Mr. Shindo in the manager's position in place of Ms. Sakurakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we have a report from Ms. Sakurakawa about this issue. Ms. Sakurakawa, go ahead, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is finally setting on her run at the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that I made Brighton's CEO angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken the necessary steps to apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Samejima Sakurakawa Law Firm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we will be merging with New York's Smith & Clark law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have consented to our firm being reinvented as a top law firm on a global scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you part of Smith & Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:05:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They were supposed to pull out of Japan.\N- As Brighton is also a worldwide firm, then I hope it will continue its contract with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just stupid! You can't make the decision to merge without consulting anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The founder and management rights of this firm still belong to...\N- Mr. Samejima also gladly sided with this proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... He had agreed to the idea of expelling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The direction the wind blows can change suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been entrusted with the full rights to manage this new Samejima Sakurakawa Smith & Clark law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, excuse me...\N- What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was brilliant. But what about Mr. Shindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitors are quickly dismissed. I'll pack my bags straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you were fired? Who would fire such a top-rate employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have prepared the position of New York representative for Mr. Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also thank you for your hard work during the 3 month trial period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to formally hire you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata's babysitter will be returning from her maternity leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to use that knowledge from babysitting as I'll be putting you in charge of Brighton's baby goods section.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you maybe have this planned from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy to be work in New York where Mr. Shindo is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did wonderfully. Splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she thought of your position too, Mr. Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should work below Ms. Sakurakawa as you aim for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right. Let's cancel our engagement too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go to New York with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Once I decide on something...\N- You won't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've chosen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was crying, you were there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also I'm a person who started from a massive defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that people who have had a taste of that pain are stronger than those who only know how to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to continue work as the loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you can change from a loser into a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been trying to gain victories since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gain those victories together. We'll strive to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the end, let's stand victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see it through to the end as we live married happily forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both become the Hawks of Manhattan together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This show is proudly brought to you by these sponsors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You'll have a subdued wedding ceremony?!\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be at Saint Patrick's Cathedral or with horse-drawn carriages or in a  twelve-layered ceremonial kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There also won't be anything similar to Kate or Diana or canons or any private jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Without any private jets either?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But haven't you already sent out the invitations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just changing the venue and scaling down the size of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of consideration for Mr. Shindo's standing, we'll hold back on the celebratory feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope my two bridesmaids don't mind the shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A surprise party?\N- Mm.\N- A surprise party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be scaling down the size of things, but I feel like I'd like to somehow respond to her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like everyone to help cooperate with me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having you say that is a great help to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel like you have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have struggled in my own ways to be standing here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this surprise idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right, thanks.\N- People have to pretend they don't know about their own surprise birthday parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent 40 years dealing with that hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.12,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will not be attending the wedding"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good evening!\N- Ah, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, are you l on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. After this place closes each day, I'll help out at Paul Bocuse. I may be putting myself under a lot of strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also I thought I should try to hone my skills a bit before I got to the main restaurant in Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't be attending their wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, I've decided to leave for Lyon that evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh?\N- I thought I'd go over there first and get things settled before I bring you over, Soyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's why you chose that day to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, no. I just thought that if I'm going, it's best to go earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also me not being there would be better for Wakaba too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're doing it for Ayukawa's sake?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going so suddenly because it's best for Ayukawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, no....\N- Don't you think that way of thinking is a bit odd?\N- No, I told you that you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll call you when I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- See you.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good work.\N- Ah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sota seems to have put a lid on his own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that he's using Soyoko to help him forget about someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was supposed to have forgotten about Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I make him only look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him so much, so what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like him, then it isn't about what you want, but about what you can do to make that other person happy. That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment, bridesmaids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll be leaving this run-down room soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soyoko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit!? Ow, that's hot! He'll quit that place and go to France?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Somehow it just feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he leave so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wrong? What feels wrong?\N- How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's like I'm sick and tired of it.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried dating him, but his kindness seems like it might just be indecisiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he really isn't thinking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Or maybe he's just lying.\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pill Bug is serious about everything he does in his own Pill Bug way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely thought properly about Soyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many people who care about others like he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... just... that he's a little bit awkward about how he does things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should definitely... definitely not let him out of your grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I knew it.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you both like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you just helped confirm my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally... I hate Sota and everything that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hang on. Listen to me properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main reason that I hate Sota is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the person who Sota likes... even now is not me, but rather you, Ayukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.49,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Sota"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Pill Bug likes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's trying hard to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.54,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"From Soyoko"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now Pill Bug likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no! Not now. This can't be happening to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't be unsure. I mustn't. Once I've decided to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3.1415926535
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always received the prizes for perfect attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning things halfway through? That's not part of my rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to always be this way. I've become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.79,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"The more tears you cry will just make you stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it. I won't feel unsure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.27,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Question yourself"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the kind of grown-up I wanted to become!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did I go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistence is important. But do I have to keep that up even if it becomes a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.83,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lies are a huge sin"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I realize that it's wrong, I should turn back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can turn back, then I want to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But adults have adult rules. There are laws we should obey.\N- To be damned with those laws!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stand up and face myself one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:29.58,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Question yourself"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Soyoko dumped you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I guess she doesn't want to go to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah.\N- So what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Today I'm helping out with the catering at Paul Bocuse, then I'm heading to Lyon on a flight this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess you won't be attending the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I don't have time. I have to be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. You're not even letting us hold a farewell party for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitaro's one was enough. Besides, there are some formalities to take care of, so I'll come back for them and we can meet up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, do you have any messages for that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick you up? I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello to her from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Send her my heartfelt congratulations.\N- Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, okay.\N- Right, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- See you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine weather, but your face doesn't seem so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if. Ah, no. I was just wondering what I'm supposed to do if I want to go to the toilet in this dress. I'm just nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and take a look at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Do you have another complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you look very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what was that about it being a fine day, but you have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about how your babysitting duties are almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only babysitter whose name I've remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess maybe you're just unforgettable because you don't always act like an adult and you're a mess at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me you are a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- At some stage you became more than just work and I developed real feelings for you.\N- Please continue with the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, there isn't much time! Hurry!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Prepare dishes for 18 people.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba, as a babysitter and as a woman, you're really useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stubborn and obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back, I realize there were so many horrible things that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, you may think innocent people can receive no blame, but you branded Pill Bug as a sexual predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:22:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Article 5-1 of the law governing disturbance of the peace!\N- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We unexpectedly met again when you were appointed as my babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you helped out with the after-school care rotation scheme, you kept saying abusive things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ideal type of man is a man with money and social status who hates children!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end you kissed him, but put the blame onto him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sue you for sexual assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sue!?\N- That's a perfect example.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata! Here's your packed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were those words you said to a man who had gathered up your spilled lunch in the rain and put it back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you dislike having to take her such an ugly lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh?\N- It's your fault that she called my bear a mouse.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your uncooperative personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention this, but I was not cooperating with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pitaro! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got covered in mud and sweat. And you smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way Wakaba works hard, makes me think that I ... like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought you'd finally figured out your own feelings, you tripped up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to get together so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still kept denying your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am neither a good person nor a good dad to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a cunning adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who you choose, Wakaba. As your dad, I will trust the choice you make, Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you are being honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked you, Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one wonderful side to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the way you always put your full effort into everything you did, whether it was for me or for someone else's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you most want to protect and look after?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.98,0:25:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I want to look after is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:17.71,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Question yourself"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.87,0:25:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one more time. Who is the most important person to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.37,0:25:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mr. Shindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.54,0:25:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the guests will already be there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell Mr. Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.29,0:26:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.11,0:26:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yamada, carry that.\N- Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.10,0:26:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I am... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.50,0:26:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shindo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:26:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.91,0:27:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing here?\N- I should be asking you that, Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.87,0:27:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Well, um... I've been helping at Paul Bocuse with the catering, so I've been in this kitchen since the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.15,0:27:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The ceremony we're catering for is yours!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.70,0:27:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Mr. Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.51,0:27:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.37,0:28:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way to New York now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh!?\N- I have to go there sooner to settle on our strategy from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.17,0:28:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final surprise present.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.64,0:28:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was defeated by Ms. Sakurakawa, you said you'd still be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.54,0:28:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first moment that I truly thought that I'd like to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.37,0:28:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply responding to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.42,0:28:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Shindo...\N- My parents accepted my decision. I've also bowed my head to the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.90,0:28:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept anything that anyone has to say about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.27,0:28:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends and I spoke about this too and we all agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly... very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be sure to work and pay off the money you gave to my father and the reparation money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.31,0:29:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... somehow... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.66,0:29:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to at least let me look cool at the end of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.11,0:29:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'll leave the rest up to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.15,0:29:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.80,0:30:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said... that a kiss isn't the start of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.64,0:31:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that was a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.50,0:31:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow things changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.95,0:31:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to... continuously care for you, Pill Bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.71,0:31:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sota,... you're the one I've been stubbornly... in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.37,0:31:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.16,0:31:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.12,0:32:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you... marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.41,0:32:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.85,0:32:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'd promised Pitaro that I wouldn't cry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.92,0:32:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will turn down your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.89,0:33:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be the one to propose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.01,0:33:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These words are a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.50,0:33:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also love you Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.94,0:33:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything great for you... but I will love you my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.23,0:33:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the one thing I'm confident about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.92,0:33:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.11,0:33:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.10,0:34:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.89,0:34:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.91,0:34:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.91,0:34:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.35,0:34:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations!\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.92,0:34:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.67,0:34:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.21,0:34:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.97,0:34:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.67,0:35:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, congratulations, Wakaba. Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.22,0:35:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokkedano. Mokkeda...\N{\b0}["Thank you" in Yamagata dialect]{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.59,0:35:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.78,0:35:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.53,0:35:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh?\N- Yay!\N- Eh? Pitaro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.80,0:35:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, dad and Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why are you here?\N- We suddenly returned to Japan because Hinata arranged it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.90,0:35:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.49,0:35:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She begged me so much that I couldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.90,0:35:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her mom make the arrangements. By private jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.91,0:35:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anyone who can beat this mother and daughter's recklessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.54,0:36:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on a pursuit for knowledge, but please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.93,0:36:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be a Pill Bug, but I will be a Pill Bug who comes back as a Pill Bug who has set his roots firmly in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.33,0:36:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.87,0:36:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Kiss! Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.95,0:36:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.95,0:36:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kiss! Kiss! Kiss!\N- Oh! He picked her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.11,0:37:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've finished sending the applications for merging to the legal committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. Well, I'm looking forward to seeing you in Japan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.87,0:37:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.66,0:37:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see your Pill Bug off at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.42,0:37:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.51,0:37:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.74,0:37:54.75,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Letter of resignation"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked out the path that I want to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.78,0:38:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good timing. The babysitter is finally back from her maternity leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.24,0:38:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be easy to find someone to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.98,0:38:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. I was starting to get bored with both you and Hinata anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.45,0:38:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only for a short time, but I'm so grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.77,0:38:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anything else you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.12,0:39:35.83,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Samejima Sakurakawa Smith & Clark Law Firm"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.21,0:39:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have all the documents for the stock listing meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.95,0:39:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, the preparations are all done.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ouch! Ouch!\N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.52,0:39:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry.\N- There are 3 more court-appointed attorney traffic cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.55,0:39:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 8 requests for insurance too and one application to open a new restaurant. I'll finish them all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.96,0:40:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will want you as their bride in those worn-out shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.21,0:40:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you have an imaginary fiancé, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.66,0:40:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not imaginary or make-believe. It's just that we made a promise not to contact each other until we achieve our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.31,0:40:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, apparently she won another huge lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.04,0:40:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She spoke to me at the meeting of legal experts the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.16,0:40:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked if Ayukawa Wakaba was working hard. How does such an important person know someone like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.20,0:40:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was her babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.57,0:40:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please offer a comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.93,0:40:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could you please give us some comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.20,0:40:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please offer a comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.36,0:40:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey! What are you doing?\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.06,0:41:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay then. Ouch, ouch.\N- Are you okay?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.36,0:41:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for us to judge the intellectual rights we are contesting right now as going well, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.95,0:41:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Do you have any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.11,0:41:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not applied for the baby powder patent in Japan yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.49,0:41:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've sent in the applications throughout Asia. We're about to explain that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.16,0:41:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your car and a first class ticket have been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.52,0:41:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How about some candy?\N- Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.61,0:41:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Peropero" candies are called lollipop candies in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.06,0:41:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see girls wearing cat ears eating a piece of candy, I'm like, "Ah, oh my..."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.84,0:41:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you tying it on?\N- Yes.\N- Do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.25,0:41:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're tying it?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.85,0:41:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey!\N- Oh, Kobato is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.80,0:42:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Some alcohol to celebrate.\N- Oh, thanks. Hey, bring out a cushion for her. Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.08,0:42:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Put on a great performance again today.\N- I will! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.53,0:42:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been seriously dating someone for a year? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.09,0:42:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... it's Bantam.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.86,0:42:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.64,0:42:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why him!?\N- He's round and cuddly like a teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.91,0:42:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry that I wasn't able to tell you earlier. Sorry.\N- Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.87,0:42:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I won't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.74,0:42:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.18,0:42:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that reminds me, were you okay with last night's homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.91,0:42:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mm, it was difficult.\N- Right? It was difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.78,0:42:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pill bug~ pill bug~ pill bug~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.49,0:42:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your boyfriend in New York again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.84,0:42:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he calls every day without fail. It's tough being loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.27,0:42:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right, shall we go?\N- Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.01,0:42:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened with your homework yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.08,0:42:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult, but I did it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.40,0:43:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is a restaurant that we helped with the remodeling permits for. I'm in the area. What was the address?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.35,0:43:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The address is 3-chome 2-bancho...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.59,0:43:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.32,0:43:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Le Chateau?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.70,0:43:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pill Bug...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.08,0:43:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a seat. You're out first customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.12,0:44:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What troubles were you wrapped up in trying to open this place?\N- I asked Samao to place that application for me.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.21,0:44:06.04,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hayashi Kobato"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.61,0:44:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon soir. {\b0}["Good evening" in French]{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.33,0:44:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.37,0:44:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy's condition has improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.49,0:44:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start with some rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.63,0:44:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. This is this restaurant's most recommended dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.60,0:44:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your far left is the Sauce de soja. It is Lyon-style rice with soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.13,0:45:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh?\N- I added basil to make it into a gelée (jelly).
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.81,0:45:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a gelée? Soy sauce on rice should be make with Japan's traditional flavorings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.81,0:45:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.54,0:45:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something I just can't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.42,0:45:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.26,0:45:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mm, it's good!\N- Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zenkai Girl" will be released on DVD and Blue-ray Box on 18 January, 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.43,0:45:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're giving away 5 copies of each of them as a present to our viewers. Please apply by phone.